# Claude Code — local scratch, in particular the git worktrees it checks out
# inside the repo. A worktree is not repo content: committing one lands as a
# gitlink (mode 160000) with no matching .gitmodules entry, so every clone gets
# an empty directory that git reports forever as an uninitialised submodule and
# that `git submodule update --init` refuses with "No url found for submodule
# path".
.claude/worktrees/
